# Secrets + headless-init settings for the local LangFuse stack.
# Loaded automatically by `docker compose` from this directory (it sits next to
# docker-compose.yml). Everything here is LOCAL-ONLY: the stack binds to
# localhost, and these credentials never leave this machine. Regenerate any
# value with `openssl rand -hex 16` if you want fresh ones.

# --- core service secrets (the # CHANGEME values from the official compose) ---
